In a 12-inch skillet over medium heat, in olive oil, saute garlic for 2 minutes. Add mushrooms; saute until tender. Add sun-dried tomatoes, Newman's Own Bombolina Pasta Sauce, wine, vinegar, and crushed red pepper; simmer 7 minutes. Add Neufchatel cheese and stir until cheese melts. Add shrimp and simmer until shrimp turns opaque throughout, about 5 minutes. Meanwhile, cook penne according to package instructions. When al dente, place in a large serving bowl. Top with shrimp, sauce, parmesan cheese, pine nuts, and parsley. Toss and serve immediately